1. to check a number palindrome. Sarika 


pseudo: 
Input num
originalNum = num
reversedNum = 0
while num > 0
    digit = num % 10
    reversedNum = reversedNum * 10 + digit
    num = num // 10
if originalNum == reversedNum
    Print("The number is a palindrome")
else
    Print("The number is not a palindrome")


pseudo routine:
 
 function FindPalindrome(num)
    originalNum = num
    reversedNum = 0
    while num > 0
        digit = num % 10
        reversedNum = reversedNum * 10 + digit
        num = num // 10
    if originalNum == reversedNum
        return True
    else
        return False
		
pseudo test:
  
  function TestFindPalindrome()
  Input num
  if FindPalindrome(num){
  print("It is a palindrome")
  }
  else{
  print("not a palindrome")
  }
